	<h1 class="title">这个设计了不起之今日最佳</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/400262/small/400262.gif?1451567609" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">沈非 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-05-17 06:45:50 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/26920/medium/26920.jpg?1463406020" alt="" />			
